<li id="cite_note-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="IPA-label IPA-label-small">Italian:</span> <span class="IPA nowrap" lang="it-Latn-fonipa"><a href="/wiki/Help:IPA/Italian" title="Help:IPA/Italian">&#91;dʒoakˈkiːno<span class="wrap"> </span>vinˈtʃɛntso<span class="wrap"> </span>raffaˈɛːle<span class="wrap"> </span>luˈiːdʒi<span class="wrap"> </span>ˈpettʃi&#93;</a></span>; English: <b>Joachim Vincent Raphael Louis Pecci</b>.</span>
